📋 DESCRIPTION
Meta-package that loads the core mediation ecosystem:
- medfit (infrastructure)
- probmed (probabilistic effect sizes)
- RMediation (confidence intervals)
- medrobust (sensitivity analysis)
- medsim (simulations)

Inspired by tidyverse and easystats ecosystems.
Version: 0.0.0.9000

